title: General View - Manhattan - Aerial View - Grand Army Plaza - Fifth Avenue - Central Park South

folder: Central Park & Entrances & The Sherman monument., Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park - Entrances:- The Sherman Monument in the Grand Army Plaza at Fifth Avenue and 59th Street. The background building is on the east side of the Avenue, between 59th and 60th Street's.

About 1905

Gift of Urbrock Collection
title: Manhattan: Central Park - Entrances - The Sherman monument.

folder: Central Park entrance at Grand Army Plaza., Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park Entrances: The Grand Army Plaza at 59th Street, showing one of the few remaining jehu's who haunt this vicinity. Fifth Avenue is across the background and the equestrian statue of General Sherman is at the right.

June 1938

George D. Chin
